                <note rend="inline" type="source">852.48/1408: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Secretary of State</gloss> to the
                        Ambassador in Spain</hi> (<persName type="to">
                        <hi rend="italic">Hayes</hi>
                    </persName>)</head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1943-01-28T19:00:00-04:00"
                            >January 28, 1943—7 p.m.</date>
                    </dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>187. Your 17, January 4, 10 a.m., and 75, January 12, midnight. This matter was
                    discussed with Ambassador Cárdenas on Tuesday on the basis of your telegrams
                    under reference.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Hull</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
